	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-122505">
	<article id="article-comment-122505">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<img alt='' src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2048%2048'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64685e9b3a38e3e6d4a0770f89bd134fcbf5418a4c15b01de45dbc01b591e393?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' decoding='async' data-lazy-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64685e9b3a38e3e6d4a0770f89bd134fcbf5418a4c15b01de45dbc01b591e393?s=48&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g"/><noscript><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64685e9b3a38e3e6d4a0770f89bd134fcbf5418a4c15b01de45dbc01b591e393?s=48&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/64685e9b3a38e3e6d4a0770f89bd134fcbf5418a4c15b01de45dbc01b591e393?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' decoding='async'/></noscript><span class="comment-author-name"><a href="http://www.thelittleblondebaker.com" class="comment-author-link" rel="external nofollow">Cara @LttleBlndeBaker</a></span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time"><a class="comment-time-link" href="https://www.gonnawantseconds.com/one-pot-burrito-bowl-recipe/#comment-122505">January 7, 2016 at 11:07 pm</a></time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I love this! We do something similar but always do everything separate. I will have to give the one bowl a try. It looks much easier. I also want to try your spice combo. We usually cheat and get a taco seasoning packet. Thanks so much I can&#8217;t wait to try this!</p>
		</div>

